snippet.title: Victory Heat Rally - Early (Pre Kickstarter) Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/skydevilpalm/victory-heat-rally

Welcome to Victory Heat Rally!

-NEO SUPER SCALER RACING-

Drift your way to the finish line in this fast paced arcade style racer with super scaler aesthetics!
Coming soon to KICKSTARTER

Currently in development by Skydevilpalm.

(This trailer is cut from various early demo builds! Not representative of the final game!)

TEAM VHR:

Programming:  @SandwichColonel

Art/Design/Direction: @skydevilpalm (@pixeldewd & @dreampathos)

Illustration/Design: @Eliz0r

Music: @RoB_KTA , @gwizofthestars

SFX: @thecactusbear

Voice  Acting: @47Mapes


LINKS

VHR Webpage - https://www.skydevilpalm.com/victory-heat-rally

Follow us on twitter - https://twitter.com/VHRgame

Download the playable demos from itch.io - https://skydevilpalm.itch.io/victory-heat-rally
